[node name="Label" parent="Notes/SecurityNote/Text" parent_id_path=PackedInt32Array(1100640809, 1120716171) index="1" unique_id=915741923]
text = "Welcome to your new security job!

Sadly our security system has broken
down last week. This means you'll be
responsible for the safety of the 
museum.

To make sure nothing gets stolen
you'll have to go around the museum
and check for any signs of a break-in.

I put together this practice course
to make you familiar with the job.

Good luck!"

