[node name="Label" parent="Notes/CheckpointNote/Text" parent_id_path=PackedInt32Array(833927950, 1120716171) index="1" unique_id=915741923]
text = "On your left you can see an open
door, window and vent. Each has 
their own number. 

During the night, if you see one of 
these open, go to the big red report
button and select the corresponding
checkpoint.

Make sure you remember
which number they have so you can
report the right one!

Go try it out for the checkpoints you
see here!"

